text: Fredlin "Fredinho" Mompremier (born 25 November 1996) is a Haitian footballer who plays as a forward for Sporting Kansas City II in the USL Championship. On February 26, 2020, he signed with USL Championship side Sporting Kansas City II. ==References== ==External links== * Category:1996 births Category:Living people Category:Association football forwards Category:Haitian footballers Category:Fairleigh Dickinson Knights men's soccer players Category:Ocean City Nor'easters players Category:Tampa Spartans men's soccer players Category:FC Tulsa players Category:Sporting Kansas City II players Category:USL Championship players Category:USL League Two players Category:Soccer players from Florida
